      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this concours-level vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This example remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a pristine exterior and a flawless interior environment. Meticulously curated and mechanically superlative, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who prioritize excellence.",
